{"tid":1434171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比警察逗唔可以錄影?","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:44:25.000Z","uid":189695,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd822cc35735c89b929a37b3788a03f7a2da3f5","tid":1434171,"uid":189695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"而家D狗周街逗人，下個可能就係你。<br />\n已經有好多片睇到連拍片都唔比又想搶你電話/鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喂，唔好影喎，收埋佢!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔比影??? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你阻住我地做野呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點阻住呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個話可以影呀 (死都唔答邊到阻住佢)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有權影架喎!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請你配合呀，你係咪阻差辦公!? 我而家比第一次警告你!!!!! <br />\n之後成班狗就係咁吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以點完美拆解呢?  <br />\n唔通要濃縮一本警察通例即場問佢邊條例寫唔影得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b0f4e77586ca61968cafc79a47281ae00c1a53","tid":1434171,"uid":275785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔好同佢嘈可唔可以影, 叫佢繼續做佢要做嘅嘢.<br />\n佢話你阻住嘅,問佢點阻."},{"pid":"cbec7b5e3fe8bfbcea4d3f32e36187b467eb2ece","tid":1434171,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"推 留名學野"},{"pid":"b66f67b33bfc90325cd88fcf6d437d31e60e3c22","tid":1434171,"uid":276273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:54:48.000Z","